  "3156330": {
    "name": "Anomaly President",
    "steam_appid": 3156330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《时空叛客 (Anomaly President)》现已推出，带来了独特的总统主题肉鸽游戏机制，你可以用最狂热的方式摧毁敌军！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的任务是推翻将世界引向灾难的总统。然而，战斗只是其中的一部分，还远远不够。为了拯救世界，你还必须参与总统竞选。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156330/extras/5b9d2ae221e2ace3fbb6c9ef627b3b70.poster.avif?t=1770196982\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156330/extras/5b9d2ae221e2ace3fbb6c9ef627b3b70.webm?t=1770196982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>白天是总统候选人，夜晚则化身为致命战士</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游走在这个充斥着混乱和腐败的世界里，你有着不一样的身份。白天，你是赢得民心的总统候选人；夜晚，你化身为正义战士，用武器摧毁由现任总统控制的犯罪集团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个怪象频发的世界里，你会遇到各种各样的敌人以及副总统首领，每位首领都有自己独特的异常能力。例如，总统的公关负责人拥有“心灵魅惑”的能力，可让别人对他产生爱慕之情，简直不可想象？！幸运的是，击败这些首领后，你就可以获取他们的异常能力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156330/extras/34fa4ba65a8442fe89c0f243ef28f1b4.poster.avif?t=1770196982\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156330/extras/34fa4ba65a8442fe89c0f243ef28f1b4.webm?t=1770196982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单打独斗寸步难行，团队支持才是竞选成功的关键</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要一个可信赖的团队来运筹竞选活动，助力你的总统竞选之路。在《时空叛客》中，挑选合适的团队至关重要！他们可以帮助你赢得竞选！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156330/extras/39f26a13e780d9cd579b6587cb426a9c.poster.avif?t=1770196982\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156330/extras/39f26a13e780d9cd579b6587cb426a9c.webm?t=1770196982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将受压迫的Fluffies加入你的团队，帮助他们争取权利。你可以将他们分配到不同的部门：一些会在选举期间为你助选，一些会升级你的装备，还有一些会在战斗中协助你。但请记住，如果你想从中受益，你必须好好照顾他们。否则，他们可能会离开你，甚至更糟的是，失去生命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>竞选总统需要一座基地</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了同时打击隐秘的犯罪集团和进行总统竞选，你需要一个能够随行的移动基地。上车吧，这就是竞选巴士的意义所在！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据你自身的风格和需求设计竞选巴士！从零开始，添加个性化的配置，打造一个量身定制的移动基地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156330/extras/32ef5deca71091727ad88854eafc7596.poster.avif?t=1770196982\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156330/extras/32ef5deca71091727ad88854eafc7596.webm?t=1770196982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选择专属自己的武器和异常能力！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会在战斗中遇到各种特殊异常升级，帮助你成为更强大的战士。你可以成为一名剑术大师，精准招架敌人，或者转变为赛博法师，运用异常力量造成大范围伤害。在《时空叛客》中，选择永远不止一个！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更棒的是，肉鸽游戏机制可以让你体验所有的选择。你可以尝试不同的能力和升级，找到最适合你的游玩风格！在《时空叛客》中，有很多发展路径可以探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156330/extras/5fa4f11009c5ed8a89d11462d0e858b5.poster.avif?t=1770196982\" width=600 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156330/extras/5fa4f11009c5ed8a89d11462d0e858b5.webm?t=1770196982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《时空叛客》期待你的加入！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >周游全国，探索新领域，赢得民众的支持，打败现任总统的帮派，把人民从暴政统治之下解放出来，最终实现复仇大计！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《时空叛客》向你发起号召！立即行动吧！</p>",
